<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(to right, #ef4444, #dc2626); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
      .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; }
      .info-box { background: white; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
      .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 150px; color: #6b7280; }
      .info-value { color: #111827; }
      .status-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
      .rejection-box { background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>✗ Demande de congé refusée</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Bonjour <%= @employee.first_name %>,</p>

      <p>Nous sommes désolés de vous informer que votre demande de congé a été <strong>refusée</strong><% if @approver.present? %> par <%= @approver.full_name %><% end %>.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Type de congé:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.leave_type_label %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Date de début:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= l(@leave_request.start_date, format: :long) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Date de fin:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= l(@leave_request.end_date, format: :long) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Nombre de jours:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><%= @leave_request.total_days %> jour(s)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Statut:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="status-badge">Refusé</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <% if @rejection_reason.present? %>
      <div class="rejection-box">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #991b1b; margin-bottom: 8px;">Motif du refus :</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #7f1d1d;"><%= @rejection_reason %></p>
      </div>
      <% end %>

      <p>Vous pouvez contacter votre responsable pour plus d'informations ou soumettre une nouvelle demande avec d'autres dates.</p>

      <p>
        Cordialement,<br>
        <strong>L'équipe Izi-RH</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> Izi-RH. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
